By":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T17:33:11.000Z","msg":"衝三小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c1bf25de1fcc553039f8fa05757c2f423ad6eec","tid":583031,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T06:53:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/29177385_238798653353113_9182985802240491520_n.jpg?oh=7a8bb2637af6380ddefedccaeeb63a5d&amp;oe=5AFFB581\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F29177385_238798653353113_9182985802240491520_n.jpg%3Foh%3D7a8bb2637af6380ddefedccaeeb63a5d%26oe%3D5AFFB581&h=23d569c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【《中英街1號》先導海報曝光！】<br />\n<br />\n◾1967年和2019年<br />\n◽兩個不同的時代<br />\n◾兩個年代的年輕人<br />\n面對社會不景或不公義，以及自身決擇的迷思⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n《中英街1號》後天便會在大阪亞洲電影節舉行全球首映禮，敬請期待！"},{"pid":"f299682d8c181ce3a57f1a7e6c9e4279ab8c0612","tid":583031,"uid":154684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T11:21:44.000Z","msg":"《中英街1號》摘大阪亞洲電影節最優秀作品獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n趙崇基昨晚現身大阪亞洲電影節「香港之夜」，同影迷交流嘅時候，講到電影可唔可以喺香港上映就感觸落淚：「聽過好多叫我放棄嘅聲音，今日終於能喺大銀幕上睇到自己嘅作品，而且喺大阪亞洲電影節舉行世界首映。」事後他受訪時稱：「估唔到一部最本土電影，世界首映唔係喺香港，而係喺日本，亦估唔到日本觀眾反應咁熱烈，唔少人都睇到感動流淚。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180317/57959969\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180317%2F57959969&d=UW%2F8ApER6lIp2DYUhoFWCy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=16038146\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180317%2F57959969&h=a08a8cb1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180317/57959969</a>"},{"pid":"ca5974aa5a1a5413b31b52a92e7f95d673231da2","tid":583031,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T15:46:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f68c8ae5a57e802f6ac0ff5266fb97ff1d2c3ccf","tid":583031,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T13:44:03.000Z","msg":"推啦屌你"},{"pid":"af288ab1c058b3cff169edffae2ddbbaed1ce0a5","tid":583031,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f68c8ae5a57e802f6ac0ff5266fb97ff1d2c3ccf","tid":583031,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T13:44:03.000Z","msg":"推啦屌你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T13:51:01.000Z","msg":"今個月31號上正場,藝術中心有兩場優先都full house,<br />\n暫時評價好兩極<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180505/58152741\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180505%2F58152741&d=UW%2F8ApER6lIp2DYUhoFWCy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=17836c45\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180505%2F58152741&h=b289bbee\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180505/58152741</a>"}]}